s can be found at woocommerce tooltip demo. 🙂 If you have any more wordpress tooltip feature request, please don&#8217;t hesitate to tell us 🙂 Thanks, have a blessed day with your family 🙂 WordPress Tooltip Support Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"Wordpress Developer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3386:\"\n<p>Hi Dear <span class=\"tooltipsall classtoolTips2\" style=\"border-bottom:2px dotted #888;\">WordPress</span> Tooltip Plugin User,</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We released a new version of wordpress tooltip plugin, in the wordpress tooltip 10.8.6, we added an woocommerce tooltip addon to support &#8220;Custom <span class=\"tooltipsall classtoolTips6\" style=\"border-bottom:2px dotted #888;\">Product</span> Tabs for WooCommerce&#8221;, to support tooltip effects in woocommerce product tabs which made by the Custom Product Tabs for WooCommerce plugin, more details can be found at <a href=\"https://tooltips.org/features-of-wordpress-tooltips-plugin/\">wordpress tooltip <span class=\"tooltipsall classtoolTips5\" style=\"border-bottom:2px dotted #888;\">features</span></a>, and demos can be found at <a href=\"https://tooltips.org/product/show-tooltips-in-woocommerce-products/\">woocommerce tooltip demo</a>. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"🙂\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any more wordpress tooltip feature request, please don&#8217;t hesitate to tell us <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"🙂\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thanks, have a ble