ore, an user told us her woocommerce tabs which generated by the  plugin &#8220;Custom Product Tabs for WooCommerce&#8221; not works well with our  wordpress woocommerce tooltip plugin, our developer analyzed the code of  the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\">wordpress</a> &#8220;Custom Product Tabs  for WooCommerce&#8221; plugin and find the reason and developed a new version  to hook filters of the plugin &#8220;Custom Product Tabs for WooCommerce&#8221;&#8230;., please check our full description at here</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress Tooltips Support </p>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"> toolTips(\'.classtoolTips2\',\'<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">We all love wordpress</h2><br/><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1514 size-medium\" src=\"https://tomas.zhu.bz/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/wordpress-bike-300x168.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" /></h2><br/>&nbsp;\'); </script><script type=\"text/javascript\"> toolTips(\'.classtoolTips5\',\'<div style=\"padding: 0 20px 20px 20px;\"><br/><h3 style=\"margin: 0 padding: 0;\">Show any content in tooltip box</h3><br/><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Wordpress <a style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-weight:bold;color: #fd7800!important;\" href=\"https://tooltips.org/\">Tooltip</a> content not just plain text, they can be video, audio/song, image/photo, advertising, links/text.</p><br/><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; padding: 0;\">Easy to manage in seting <span class=\"tooltipsall classtoolTips9\" style=\"border-bottom:2px dotted #888;\">panel</span></h3><br/><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">In setting panel, you can add/edit/delete any tooltips, you can add new tooltips categories, assign tooltips to categories.</p><br/></div>\'); </script><script type=\"text/javascript\"> toolTips(\'.classtoolTips6\',\'<a href=\"https://tomas.zhu.bz/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/ben-white-179058.png\"><img src=\"https://tomas.zhu.bz/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/ben-white-179058.pn