ing well and have happy weekend with your family <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"🙂\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<p>We are happy to report you that we released wordpress tooltip glossary plugin 10.6.2, in this version WordPress Tooltip Glossary Plugin Support Self-Closing Shortcode and Enclosing Shortcode, with Enclosing Shortcode, you can add icon tooltips now, please check our <strong><a href=\"https://tooltips.org/wordpress-tooltip-plugin/wordpress-tooltip-plugin-document/\">icon tooltip demo</a></strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thanks, have a blessed day with your family 🙂</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress Tooltip Glossary Plugin Support Team</p>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"> toolTips(\'.classtoolTips2\',\'<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">We all love wordpress</h2><br/><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1514 size-medium\" src=\"https://tomas.zhu.bz/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/wordpress-bike-300x168.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" /></h2><br/>&nbsp;\'); </script><script type=\"text/javascript\"> toolTips(\'.classtoolTips5\',\'<div style=\"padding: 0 20px 20px 20px;\"><br/><h3 style=\"margin: 0 padding: 0;\">Show any content in tooltip box</h3><br/><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Wordpress <a style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-weight:bold;color: #fd7800!important;\" href=\"https://tooltips.org/\">Tooltip</a> content not just plain text, they can be video, audio/song, image/photo, advertising, links/text.</p><br/><h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; padding: 0;\">Easy to manage in seting <span class=\"tooltipsall classtoolTips9\" style=\"border-bottom:2px dotted #888;\">panel</span></h3><br/><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">In setting panel, you can add/edit/delete any tooltips, you can add new tooltips categories, assign tooltips to categories.</p><br/></div>\'); </script>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b